At the end of interviews, you'll often be asked: 'Do you have any questions for us?'

**Excellent questions to ask**:
'What does a typical day look like in this role?'
'What are the biggest challenges facing this team?'

00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:30.000
'How do you measure success in this position?'
'What opportunities are there for professional development?'
'What do you enjoy most about working here?'

These questions show you're engaged and serious about the role.

